name                py-tifffile
version             2021.6.6
revision            0
platforms           darwin
license             BSD
maintainers         {mps @Schamschula} openmaintainer

categories-append   science
description         Store numpy data arrays in TIFF files.
long_description    {*}${description} Read image and metadata from TIFF-like files used in \
                    bioimaging.

